text: I BOUGHT A USED IPHONE 6S PLUS AND THEY TOLD ME IT WAS UNLOCKED AND OFF COURSE IT WASNT AND THEY ALREADY LEFT I THOUGHT I JUST LOST MY MONEY FOR A PHONE I COULDNT USE, WELL I DID SOME GOOGLING AND READING REVIEWS ABOUT THIS WEBSITE, THEN I JUST GAVE IN WHAT THE HECK ITS ONLY $28 BUCKS IM LOSING WELL THE TIME FRAME WAS 2-5 DAYS MINE WAS THE EARLY MORNING OF THE 6TH DAY I WATCHED THE PERCENT THING EVERY DAY ALL DAY HOPING IT WILL UNLOCK FASTER. BUT I FINALLY GOT THE CODE AND IT WAS SIMPLE POP THE SIM CARD IN LOG IN TO YOUR ICLOUD AND BAM YOUR PHONE IS UNLOCK WITH A DIFFERENT CARRIER, DONT SECOND GUESS THIS COMPANY THEY ARE AMAZING AND ARE WORTH IT.
